00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:53.379
That motion to prevent them from reading it.

00:15:53.379 --> 00:15:57.600
Then a right-footed out-to-in mid-range shot.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:16:00.940
That's you, going for the kill.

00:16:00.940 --> 00:16:02.940
Rin!

00:16:02.940 --> 00:16:05.940
Oh!

00:16:05.940 --> 00:16:09.240
Five minutes, then the first half's done.

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:11.240
Let's close with plan B.

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:12.740
Hi-ya, Rin, sir.

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:14.240
Man, are you annoying.

00:16:14.240 --> 00:16:15.659
Well, we took the lead.

00:16:15.659 --> 00:16:18.159
Nice work acting as bait, Izuki.

00:16:18.159 --> 00:16:19.779
Damn it.

00:16:19.779 --> 00:16:22.920
Next time, I'm gonna score.

00:16:22.920 --> 00:16:24.120
What's with them?

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:25.620
Really?

00:16:25.620 --> 00:16:27.460
Damn, Momo.

00:16:27.460 --> 00:16:29.300
It's my fault.

00:16:29.300 --> 00:16:30.800
They got by me.

00:16:30.800 --> 00:16:33.960
If you couldn't stop it, I guess there was no helping it.

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:35.800
Plus, it was 2-1-1.

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:37.139
Huh.

00:16:37.139 --> 00:16:38.300
That kid.

00:16:38.300 --> 00:16:41.300
Guess he really is the brother of a genius.

00:16:41.300 --> 00:16:46.220
How many times are you going to miss, you idle-marrying hack?

00:16:46.220 --> 00:16:47.220
Huh?

00:16:47.220 --> 00:16:48.220
Look!

00:16:48.220 --> 00:16:51.980
This is what happens when you have a chance to score and mess it up.

00:16:51.980 --> 00:16:55.700
You brought this situation on all of us, worthless striker.

00:16:55.700 --> 00:16:56.920
I...

00:16:56.919 --> 00:16:58.259
Close your eyes!

00:16:58.259 --> 00:17:00.259
Yeah, they might have stolen the ball from me,

00:17:00.259 --> 00:17:02.839
but it's not like everything that went wrong is my fault.

00:17:02.839 --> 00:17:04.139
Don't blame me.

00:17:04.139 --> 00:17:06.480
Stop passing the buck.

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:11.139
This is an order from the person out here creating chances for you.

00:17:11.139 --> 00:17:13.759
Just score a goal.

00:17:13.759 --> 00:17:18.019
Because if we lose, the U-20s will be taken over by them.

00:17:18.019 --> 00:17:23.899
Though, not like I care either way.

00:17:23.899 --> 00:17:26.039
I won't let it end like this.

00:17:26.039 --> 00:17:26.839
Feel free to use it.

00:17:26.839 --> 00:17:27.759
I'll be here to help.

00:17:27.759 --> 00:17:28.759
Just give me a minute, Sigh.

00:17:28.759 --> 00:17:29.759
Maybe I could move up a position.

00:17:29.759 --> 00:17:30.759
There's time.

00:17:30.759 --> 00:17:31.759
Yep.

00:17:31.759 --> 00:17:32.759
Let's tie the first half.

00:17:32.759 --> 00:17:37.039
Now you've got to rocket up your asses.

00:17:37.039 --> 00:17:38.939
It's about time.

00:17:38.939 --> 00:17:40.759
Let's go, guys.

00:17:40.759 --> 00:17:43.659
Pretend this half is the only time we've got.

00:17:43.659 --> 00:17:52.379
And it's either victory or death.

00:17:52.379 --> 00:17:53.839
Only a few minutes left.

00:17:53.839 --> 00:17:54.959
Prior to kickoff, no one even questioned if the U-20s might lose.

00:17:54.959 --> 00:17:55.959
I'm not.

00:17:55.959 --> 00:17:56.720
I'm not.

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:59.440
I never thought we'd ever lose.

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:00.440
But now we consider.

00:18:00.440 --> 00:18:01.440
Will the Blue Lock 11 be able to stave off the U-20's attacks?

00:18:01.440 --> 00:18:02.440
And come out on top in the first half?

00:18:02.440 --> 00:18:03.440
Alright.

00:18:03.440 --> 00:18:09.640
They've put more players on the attack.

00:18:09.640 --> 00:18:22.700
Plus, with Sai Itoshi at the nucleus, they're using short passes to inch a field!

00:18:22.700 --> 00:18:24.400
Man, they're way more desperate then before!

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:25.400
They're here!

00:18:25.400 --> 00:18:25.519
Huh?

00:18:25.519 --> 00:18:26.519
What?!

00:18:26.519 --> 00:18:28.019
Get ready, Wing!

00:18:28.019 --> 00:18:30.019
Yep, I'm all over it.

00:18:30.019 --> 00:18:33.519
Bring it on, you geckering fox.

00:18:33.519 --> 00:18:36.519
That was the plan all along, Buzzy B.

00:18:36.519 --> 00:18:38.019
This way!

00:18:38.019 --> 00:18:40.019
That's what you were after?

00:18:40.019 --> 00:18:43.019
You think you're the only team that changed tactics?

00:18:43.019 --> 00:18:46.019
To keep the lead for these last five minutes,

00:18:46.019 --> 00:18:49.019
we'll leave Nagi up front and pull everyone else back.

00:18:49.019 --> 00:18:51.019
A total defense formation!

00:18:51.019 --> 00:18:56.019
This is Blue Lock's strategy for winning with a team made up exclusively of forwards.

00:18:56.019 --> 00:18:57.019
Plan B!

00:18:57.019 --> 00:18:59.019
Steel Batsuna, two on one!

00:18:59.019 --> 00:19:00.519
I'm on it!

00:19:00.519 --> 00:19:02.019
Kitsune!

00:19:02.019 --> 00:19:03.019
Two.

00:19:03.019 --> 00:19:04.019
Together!

00:19:04.019 --> 00:19:06.019
Super fantastic timing.

00:19:06.019 --> 00:19:08.019
You can do it, Cho!

00:19:08.019 --> 00:19:10.019
I will.

00:19:10.019 --> 00:19:11.019
Trust me.

00:19:11.019 --> 00:19:13.019
I don't think so.

00:19:13.019 --> 00:19:15.019
Nice, Niko.

00:19:16.019 --> 00:19:19.019
Thanks to your tackle, his options were narrowed.

00:19:19.019 --> 00:19:21.019
Now I can read it.

00:19:21.019 --> 00:19:22.519
What, you!

00:19:22.519 --> 00:19:24.019
Nice save, man!

00:19:24.019 --> 00:19:26.019
It's not dead, second ball!

00:19:26.019 --> 00:19:28.019
One minute of additional time!

00:19:28.019 --> 00:19:29.019
Don't let off!

00:19:29.019 --> 00:19:30.019
Hey!

00:19:30.019 --> 00:19:31.019
Watch out!

00:19:37.019 --> 00:19:38.019
Get on him!

00:19:38.019 --> 00:19:40.019
Don't let him get any closer!

00:19:40.019 --> 00:19:41.019
Sandwich him!

00:19:41.019 --> 00:19:42.019
Got you!

00:19:44.019 --> 00:19:45.019
Over there?

00:19:46.019 --> 00:19:47.019
No!

00:19:48.019 --> 00:19:49.019
So fast.

00:19:49.019 --> 00:19:51.019
Wait, he's going between us?

00:19:52.019 --> 00:19:54.019
I'm not going to let him get away!

00:19:54.019 --> 00:19:55.019
I'm going to get him!

00:19:56.019 --> 00:19:58.019
He's too good!

00:20:04.019 --> 00:20:06.019
That's a nasty cross.

00:20:06.019 --> 00:20:08.019
There's no way I can reach it.

00:20:09.019 --> 00:20:10.019
No!

00:20:10.019 --> 00:20:11.019
I have to!

00:20:11.019 --> 00:20:13.019
I'll be the hero!

00:20:13.019 --> 00:20:15.019
Epic.

00:20:17.019 --> 00:20:20.019
The best in the world with a pass like that.

00:20:20.019 --> 00:20:22.019
You've lost the right to use the Shido!

00:20:27.019 --> 00:20:28.019
That'll do.

00:20:28.019 --> 00:20:29.019
Perfect.

00:20:31.019 --> 00:20:33.019
Stop interrupting.

00:20:35.019 --> 00:20:37.019
You're such a pain, little brother.

00:20:38.019 --> 00:20:40.019
I'll get you, you little...

00:20:40.019 --> 00:20:41.019
I'll get you, you little...

00:20:53.019 --> 00:20:54.019
My time...

00:20:54.019 --> 00:20:55.019
to shine!

00:20:56.019 --> 00:20:57.019
I'll get you, you little...

00:20:57.019 --> 00:20:58.019
followed by this ball...

00:20:59.019 --> 00:21:00.019
Hyundai has won it this hour.

00:21:00.019 --> 00:21:01.019
They did it!

00:21:04.019 --> 00:21:07.019
Ready?

00:21:07.019 --> 00:21:09.019
My turn?

00:21:09.019 --> 00:21:12.019
Shoot the ball to the offensive line to score!

00:21:14.019 --> 00:21:15.019
What an exciting shift!

00:21:16.019 --> 00:21:18.019
And now let's see what you do before the run!

00:21:18.019 --> 00:21:19.019
Bye-bye, revelation, fake!

00:21:19.019 --> 00:21:20.019
You guys are the best!

00:21:20.019 --> 00:21:21.019
Good game!

00:21:21.019 --> 00:21:22.019
Have a great night!

00:21:22.019 --> 00:21:23.019
Do it again!

00:21:23.019 --> 00:21:24.019
Everybody go, too!

00:21:24.019 --> 00:21:25.019
What?

00:21:55.019 --> 00:22:25.000
I love you.

00:22:25.019 --> 00:22:55.000
I love you.

00:22:55.019 --> 00:23:25.000
I love you.

00:23:25.019 --> 00:23:25.779
It's Bone.

00:23:25.980 --> 00:23:27.500
You heard it here first!

00:23:27.759 --> 00:23:28.680
What is the hell?

00:23:28.799 --> 00:23:30.339
Let's hear the professor's explanation!

00:23:30.980 --> 00:23:34.559
Of art we ask, has the artist poured their soul into it?

00:23:35.160 --> 00:23:37.779
Yet this piece reeks of being sculpted as an investment.

00:23:38.519 --> 00:23:39.160
Therefore, Bone.

00:23:39.480 --> 00:23:40.660
Thank you very much for coming.

00:23:40.879 --> 00:23:41.420
Take care now.

00:23:41.740 --> 00:23:43.279
Next exhibitor, please!

00:23:43.299 --> 00:23:45.319
Torimo Ikirashi, Aichi Prefecture.

00:23:45.779 --> 00:23:49.639
This is a scroll handed down for generations at the temple my family runs.

00:23:49.799 --> 00:23:54.259
It's precious to my parents, so I am hoping that the professor and all his infinite wisdom will grant it a knock.

00:23:54.259 --> 00:23:54.559
What?

00:23:54.559 --> 00:23:57.279
Sorry, but it's a fugazi, Buzzcut.

00:23:57.619 --> 00:24:00.759
People will think your family's so dumb you can't even spot a forgery.

00:24:01.139 --> 00:24:03.859
I advise you throw it away immediately, you dim-witted dingus.

00:24:04.379 --> 00:24:06.099
Thank you very much for playing!

00:24:06.579 --> 00:24:09.559
And now would our final exhibitor please step up!

00:24:09.859 --> 00:24:10.839
I've brought treasures.

00:24:11.220 --> 00:24:13.099
The Meguru Bachira Collection.

00:24:13.240 --> 00:24:13.440
What?

00:24:14.039 --> 00:24:15.839
My, what do we have here?

00:24:16.159 --> 00:24:18.000
Acorns I picked up while dribbling.

00:24:18.119 --> 00:24:22.599
Along with nice looking rocks, some marbles, and my baby teeth.

00:24:22.839 --> 00:24:24.000
This one's a molar.

00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:25.279
This one's a front tooth.

00:24:25.279 --> 00:24:28.880
And now, Professor Karasu, would you please appraise their value?

00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:30.380
Knot bone!

00:24:30.380 --> 00:24:31.680
I knew it! Awesome!

00:24:31.680 --> 00:24:32.779
Hooray!

00:24:32.779 --> 00:24:33.980
What? And how?

00:24:33.980 --> 00:24:35.380
So you don't know.

00:24:36.019 --> 00:24:39.380
To achieve knot bone, you must be fully immersed in ego.

00:24:39.380 --> 00:24:42.619
It's a passion and experience not seen anywhere else in the world.

00:24:42.619 --> 00:24:44.619
Pursuing that is what it means to be knot bone.

00:24:44.619 --> 00:24:45.380
I have no idea.

00:24:45.380 --> 00:24:48.720
You see, there are eight billion types of knot bone.

00:24:48.720 --> 00:24:50.220
See you all next week!

00:24:50.220 --> 00:24:51.819
B-b-b-bone!

00:24:51.819 --> 00:24:53.460
Three nights in a row, too.

00:24:53.460 --> 00:24:54.460
The same dream!

00:24:54.460 --> 00:24:54.960
Knot bone!

00:24:54.960 --> 00:24:55.960
B-b-b-bone!

